'''''elf''''' is a [[Gnomish]] word meaning "five".<ref name=PE11>{{PE|11}}, p. 53</ref> While appearing without any designated language in the source, [[Patrick H. Wynne]] has drawn the conclusion that the word is Gnomish.<ref name=VT>{{VT|48a}}, p. 20 (note 17)</ref>

==Etymology==

*[[Sundocarme|Root]] [[LEP#Other versions|''lef-'']] ("half")<ref name=PE11/>

==Cognates==

*[[Qenya]] ''[[lemin|lempe]]''<ref name=PE11/>
